The Bloomsburg Fair Association is returning its profits from the helicopter rides to Enlow's widow, Connie Enlow. He is also survived by two siblings.

'The fair board is going to do whatever we can to help her with whatever she needs,' said Barratt.

Montour County Coroner Scott Lynn told the Bloomsburg Press-Enterprise the Birdsboro man's death is under investigation.

